snippet.title: ASCENDANT | Full Trailer | NEXT FEST 2024
snippet.description:
Damn, gorl... (izard), it's the FULL Trailer! 

Forget fresh air and that inner voice telling you to "go outside" because you can dive in on all the neon-soaked, biopunk madness ALL WEEK LONG during Steam Next Fest, from Monday, October 14th.

► Wishlist on Steam now! https://bit.ly/4hakIZK

ASCENDANT is a squad-based tactical FPS with serious balls. Each match is different, with game-changing events and adrenaline-fueled battles. Set in a dynamic BioPunk world where everything wants to kill you; fight to extract resources, and get out with more than just your dignity.
